---
import EthanMorales from "../../assets/testimonial/ethan-morales.jpg";
import Scroll from "./TestimonialsScroll.svelte";
import Testimonial from "../ui/Testimonial.astro";
---

<section
  class="bg-linear-to-b from-[#F8FAF4] from-[0%] to-white to-[100%] py-10 sm:py-20"
>
  <h2
    class="text-h3 sm:text-h2 intersect-once intersect:animate-slide-in mb-3 text-center font-medium"
  >
    Why they love us
  </h2>
  <p
    class="text-muted-foreground intersect-once intersect:animate-slide-in motion-delay-100 mb-12 text-center text-lg"
  >
    Quotes from our customers
  </p>
  <Scroll client:load>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Ethan Morales"
      role="CTO at Carbonfact"
    >
      Let's put it straight: 70% less audit prep, dozens of eng hours back. ROI
      day one, Probo was a no brainer investment.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Sarah Chen"
      role="VP Engineering at DataCore"
    >
      aze
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Marcus Johnson"
      role="Head of Security at Streamline"
    >
      Finally, a tool that actually understands developer workflow. Security
      compliance without the headache.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Priya Patel"
      role="CTO at FinanceHub"
    >
      Our compliance costs dropped 60% in the first quarter. The platform pays
      for itself before the trial even ends.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="James O'Brien"
      role="Director of Engineering at CloudWave"
    >
      Probo turned our biggest operational bottleneck into our smoothest
      process. Audit season is no longer a nightmare.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Ana Rodriguez"
      role="VP of Compliance at SecureOps"
    >
      Three audits passed with zero findings. That's never happened before
      Probo. This tool is legitimately game-changing.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="David Kim"
      role="CTO at GrowthTech"
    >
      We scaled from 10 to 100 engineers without scaling our compliance team.
      Probo made that possible.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Rachel Thompson"
      role="Head of Platform at Nexus"
    >
      Real-time visibility into our compliance posture changed everything. We
      catch issues before they become problems.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Michael Zhang"
      role="VP Engineering at Catalyst"
    >
      Implementation took two days. Results were immediate. Best tooling
      decision we made this year, hands down.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Lauren Martinez"
      role="CTO at Velocity Systems"
    >
      Our auditors were impressed with the documentation quality. Probo
      generates better reports than we ever could manually.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Tom Andersson"
      role="Director of Infrastructure at CloudScale"
    >
      85% reduction in compliance overhead. Our engineers can finally focus on
      building instead of box-checking.
    </Testimonial>
    <Testimonial
      image={EthanMorales}
      author="Olivia Wright"
      role="VP of Engineering at DataShield"
    >
      We were drowning in compliance debt. Probo pulled us out in weeks, not
      months. Absolute lifesaver.
    </Testimonial>
  </Scroll>
</section>
